social_posts.post_text: Today is all about you @austincassim , my not so baby brother, my best friend, my right hand man and my partner in crime! Wishing you a blessed birthday and many more prosperous years! Every year you continue to impress me as you grow and become a more and more successful young man. Your aptitude for life, your regard for your family and friends and the way you do business is admirable. I love you more than you know and only pray for Gods richest blessings upon you! Cheers to your birthday week 🍾❤️ swipe to slide 3 to see how @ciniminmusic was formed.
If that’s how this week kicked off then we in for a big one! Thanks @litchiparty ❤️ also shout out to the dude crowd surfing in the first video! 😂
Season has started! 🍾

Opening night of @ballitorage 2022

Should we release this @ciniminmusic track?

What do put on your pancakes? CINIMIN! 😏
Come get your  exclusive @ciniminmusic merchandise at the @ballitorage Sound factory from tonight! There’s limited stock so make sure you get there early! We’re on at 8pm on the mega dome.

Ultimate Dj reunion @ballitorage 

So good seeing all the boys in one place! 🍾🎉

Our 2022 season of @jozisundays comes to an end this weekend. Joined by all your favorite resident DJs we welcome my good friend @timoodv to the stage! A day into night party filled with deep house, Afro tech and some melodic techno… it’s going to be the perfect year end party! See you on Sunday! @joziginbryanston

Last night we had the privilege of having an honorary dinner with the legendary founder of @defectedrecords , mr @simondunmore1 . Defected records is one of the main reasons I became a Dj as they paved the way for house music since 1999. From ‘ Sunday shouting ‘ to ‘ Finally’ to records like ‘ Hey hey ‘ and ‘ At night ‘. These are just a few tracks that inspired me to become a Dj and invoke my passion for house music! Long live defected and long live house music! ❤️ big shout and and thank you to @ricardodacosta_ for hosting us🍾🙏

From my family to yours, we truly hope you had a blessed Christmas! As a Christian today is an important day to us, we come together to celebrate the birth of Jesus Christ and more importantly what he came down to teach us all. Love each other as he loves us! Sending love to every single one of you!🎄❤️

Last stretch of gigs for 2022, 8 shows in Cape Town, 1 show in Plett and 3 in Durban all coming up this week! Thank you for the tremendous support this year I look forward to seeing a lot of you at these parties ( swipe right ) this week. 

Kicking off the week with a set at Corona sunsets feat @goldfishlive at the @grandafricacafeandbeach as well as a set at @clubparadise_sa

One of the coolest campaigns I’ve seen in a while! The #stimrolflowlab is LIVE! Help us find South Africa’s next super star! All you gotta do is download the @5fm app and get voting! Plus you stand a chance to win R5000, and we all know we need it after this December! For more information and Ts & Cs go check out the 5fm app!

Last shows for 2022 tonight. Now unless you’re in JHB you have no excuse to come say good bye to 2022 with me as I’ll be in Cape Town and Durban this evening!

Final gig of the season! Oh and what a season it was! 3 countries, 6 provinces, 35 shows, ALL OF YOU DANCING! 

I’m taking a two week break now to reset and plan for 2023! I’ll see you back on the dance floor at the end of Jan! 

Thank you @goldfishlive @anythinggoessa @wearemusicpeople for having me last night!

Hello from Zanzibar! 🏝️ 
Or as the Tanzanians say ‘Jambo 👋’

And we’re home! Zanzibar you were to good to us! I needed a rest after season and that’s exactly what I got! 😴

From making new friends, having naps on the beach, drinking litres of local beer, snorkelling with fish 🐠 and turtles🐢, platters of fresh seafood and just taking some time to reflect on my year! I’m ever so grateful! 

A few days of chilling at home then it’s back into the swing of things.

We have some really exciting news! 🎉The CINIMIN Family is growing! We’ve decided to up our game and expand the team! We would like to formally introduce you to Kaira Liddell. Anything you need in terms of information, bookings, campaigns, influencing etc for Kyle Cassim, Austin Cassim and Cinimin you can now contact her! She’s amazing at her job and we’re so excited for you to meet her! 

Swipe for all the email and telephone information 💪❤️

You can also mail lea@flipsidemanagement.co.za for bookings @flipsidemanagement

To my beautiful Valentine. This is the last time I wish you a happy valentines as a fiancé! Next year this time you’ll be my wife. Thank you for your unconditional love and caring for me so much. I appreciate you more than you know. Here’s to many more ❤️

Today is about you and only you. I honestly feel so blessed to be able to share a third birthday with you in a row. The most beautiful woman that I have ever laid eyes on and yet you have the softest, kindest and most caring soul. Thank you for being you and for being my rock! You are the ultimate blessing in my life and I can’t wait to share a million more birthdays with you! Happy birthday my baby girl! I love you ❤️ @nixmarelsh

Happy birthday to my beautiful mother! We hope your day is as amazing as you are! Thank you for showering us daily with your love, kindness and delicious food! We are eternally grateful for you! We pray God continues to bless you all the days of your life. Love you always

Good Friday. The day that changed the world forever. 
A benchmark in the Christian faith, the day Jesus gave his life for our sins. An important thing today is the symbol of forgiveness. If God could forgive the world,who are we not to forgive those around us. So my message today is to be kind to one another, love one another and forgive one another as Jesus has forgiven us. Have a blessed weekend!❤️

Woke up this morning and realised my baby bunny sister is no longer a baby. I can’t believe you are already 30! Nothing makes me happier to know you have grown into the amazing woman that you are. You are my first ever best friend and have been there for me in every step of my life. Thank you for being the loving, supporting and caring sister you are! I pray God continues to bless you everyday, what I do know is that he has the most incredible plans for the rest of your life! I love you always ❤️ @danielle_cassim

New year new project. 
I’ve teamed up with the guys from one of the institutions of clubs in South Africa @onyx_nightclub to bring back proper clubbing on a Thursday night. 

When I was ( a bit ) younger, Thursdays were always a night to get dressed up and go out and listen to our Favorite house, hip hop and rnb. 

I feel like that part of the jhb scene has been slacking for a while so it’s time to bring it back. 

With a selection of your Favorite Hip hop and house Headline acts from South Africa we’re we’re gonna be turning up every Thursday! 

Once again it’s not necessarily about being under ground or commercial but more about a proper club experience with good music, good people and lots of tequila. 

Launching 11 May with my guest @djmilkshake , @johnlyra , @austincassim @justlensofficial @marcothedj

Looking back at this year and I’ve never felt this blessed! 

From my growth in my career to my realtionship with my wife , family and friends to my mental and physical health to my overall happiness, it’s been a good year! 

Started off with me playing on the MainStage of @ultrasouthafrica to becoming an ambassador for @karllagerfeld @preview_designer_collection to having 2500 people at my birthday party @truthjhb to going to Ibiza for my bachelors then marrying my dream woman to having the most amazing honeymoon in Italy. It continued with playing at some of the most epic festivals including a sold out @goldfishlive show in Amsterdam to celebrating 7 years of The Kyle Cassim Show on @5fm . 

I need to say a big thank you to everyone that supports me from the fans, festival promoters, club owners, family and friends, nothing would be possible without you. And of course all Glory goes to God, I am where am because of your hand upon me and your blessings! 

Cheers to an even bigger 2024!
